<subSubSection id="C350656FAE31FFA8FF253FACFC83D45D" pageId="7" pageNumber="560" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="8BF536E4AE31FFA8FF253FACFC83D45D" blockId="7.[151,1437,151,1365]" pageId="7" pageNumber="560">
<emphasis id="B93EEAF6AE31FFA8FF253FACFED1D585" bold="true" box="[199,315,1231,1257]" pageId="7" pageNumber="560">Remarks.</emphasis>
The new species is similar to 
<taxonomicName id="4C4A4D67AE31FFA8FD713FACFCADD584" box="[659,839,1231,1257]" class="Insecta" family="Hybotidae" genus="Oedalea" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="7" pageNumber="560" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="vietnamensis">
<emphasis id="B93EEAF6AE31FFA8FD713FACFCADD584" box="[659,839,1231,1257]" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="560">O. vietnamensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, but may be separated from the latter by pedicel and first flagellomere paler than scape (pedicel paler than first flagellomere and scape 
<taxonomicName id="4C4A4D67AE31FFA8FBAB3F90FB14D460" box="[1097,1278,1267,1293]" class="Insecta" family="Hybotidae" genus="Oedalea" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="7" pageNumber="560" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="vietnamensis">
<emphasis id="B93EEAF6AE31FFA8FBAB3F90FB14D460" box="[1097,1278,1267,1293]" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="560">O. vietnamensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
); pterostigma slightly short, suboval; left surstylus distinctly widened apically.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="C350656FAE31FFA8FF253E58FC67D439" box="[199,909,1339,1365]" pageId="7" pageNumber="560" type="etymology">
